<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6;">

    <h2>Hello {{ owner_name }},</h2>

    <p>
        We have reviewed the documents submitted for your restaurant
        <strong>{{ restaurant_name }}</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
        Unfortunately, the following document could not be approved:
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>{{ document_name }}</strong>
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>Reason for rejection:</strong>
    </p>

    <blockquote style="margin:16px 0;padding:12px 16px;border-left:4px solid #dc3545;background:#f8f9fa;">
        {{ reason }}
    </blockquote>

    <p>
        Please review the feedback above, update the document if necessary,
        and upload a new version through the FoodRush dashboard.
    </p>

    <p>
        Once resubmitted, our team will review it as soon as possible.
    </p>

    <p>
        Thank you for choosing <strong>FoodRush</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
        Best regards,<br />
        <strong>FoodRush Team</strong>
    </p>

</body>

</html>